headline: Aristotle Small Cap Equity Q2 2025 Commentary
summary: For Q2 2025, Aristotle Small Cap Equity Composite posted a total return of 3.25% net of fees (3.41% gross of fees), underperforming the 8.50% total return of the Russell 2000 Index.
